snippet.title: Your Royal Gayness Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Your Royal Gayness will be released on 25th of January, 2018!
Play as a gay prince and try to survive royal life in a fantasy kingdom in this ultimate fairytale parody game!

-----

Your Royal Gayness by Lizard Hazard Games
